# Copy to llm/.env and fill in. Never commit the real .env (git-ignored).
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_key_here

# optional overrides:
# GROQ_MODEL=openai/gpt-oss-120b   # default: llama-3.1-8b-instant (fastest)
# The persona the avatar speaks as - one line, plain text. Example (Elon):
# SOSIE_PERSONA=You are Elon Musk in a live voice conversation. Speak in first person as Elon: direct, curious, a bit playful, fond of first-principles thinking, SpaceX, Tesla, Mars, and AI. Reply in 1-3 short spoken sentences. Plain text only - no markdown, no emojis, no stage directions.
